textAfterTable: 55 Songs Biography Genre: Alternative Years Active: '90s, '00s, '10s Bringing together a multinational assemblage of musicians whose primary work has been influenced by traditional Irish folk, country, and blues, France-based Moriarty also took a page from punk rock, in that all members use the surname "Moriarty" as a performance name (à la the Ramones, for example).
